ji6VkiHGaQ80NLx3-66Ag/Y0ptH_juzLi7Bwo3_fZ95f0VRAdWrsiw/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="艾米丽·比索 |布隆伯格"&gt;艾米丽·比索&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;地球变暖的速度比以往任何时候都快，与此同时，极端天气也在加剧。在这些事件中，几乎一半涉及洪水。因此，为了保护世界沿海城市以及居住在其中的数亿居民，工程师们正在创造一些独特的（在许多情况下是巨大的）解决方案。从&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/V9jCkkgmOPfrpog69gZ_oD6xEXqzDmAPHEPGzr-O0gxoF2Uyf1BWZkSQXF9A51iXyVd7mxr_b0ynQITJn_rGdTHb00JN8sUDFkD3MiZfyMUSz0fpZ0McJUm3qNvY8GGmSBdAmE6VC_ffQEkXwWT4_6zJyRu44lSjaDWqwi607CTijHpzNKJjLKhju2tlMgyXRjUeABjuI8k6Pln7vS_kDwf9wM9sZT14CUS-nPhkalgD500JNPveiSSFSIHaeI35U9K-EbQSVX9NflpabPw2vLTQk3cjyY0lt8wiDt59LLcjOhhUNfSCrREFsi50jvCTgjMtic6KGEjmdA_PPqdnxbJm2Y-lmNjCkFondMzaALs1QCnm4IuclZVjHsvgiwPg3Kqh0K9Uk6w52XJ1Ys0NO7BXvjEFN3_AWASbGofrskP7PosKFd2pEYcyTLyHmta5uv3zF3OpLsCt4M6oWnF9vzz-SsVu23sXfV3pGmWuqDS8Pxqfebem0DE81tjG29jTEAiU8ZSu04PU6iczmd1dtrRyTHLMy78Xt217B-lQUft-R5nt5tb9ckVA8W1UOA/yXvR2KSNv5WzebEGRmVxDrTA2ceoUI_Y/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="气候变化将考验东京世界级的防洪能力"&gt;航天飞机大小的&lt;/a&gt;洪水隧道到&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/w8wwA80lyAihJ8a4Cz0sSPjW3WaON2OL5kwxGCaLKSRjDY44PxqtFzoilA-_8Sd_HDWMq9Nx4vqKa6vn8iYMPrdffybxhFC0STtWMjmsMuM4vqTqS00DL6NoJVSqZvtB5GrvZojC-yf6O_88RPGq5ooyuwGg4bca_MiC9ox8E5HBH4BfWh5bu6LBJ6ZY1mHf0icJJQgj41d4fFu8-xL7sjjDs7LxUf7nAQMKZiovx9QraBHOrkQI-VJnEPKg6NSSTF2xT1vxK6PiiHhmuzIOkjBB3Pib79mPDXYqOonZjTpFtpCLwdtizl_epnZDIhyQrjYR2yoMR_BQtmtY-wAg6qYHSjRRMyCmcmKoiT89jRArmkTqiCxrV4dXzYvjRpI0IxpWRd8csYvYBW2pEWOIdD6CVzhU7WN4ZhPCcdPUaT_Tci9PzLAsM68IfehjJMTarMhYY9xs2HVNk6tMVmE9jSOtiufVqx8BFeINQ3bh1PYlKmbtjw-gal0B4RYgw4Oi7SF6f-iexc98CFmDKXEV_UTq86Bj8MFW3yJp-id7lP4Uwgkv0488cZZX/KgN9dEYCMMJWLeitLpZV0yi4kteqdfX1/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="印度尼西亚计划开始建造耗资 800 亿美元的巨型海堤"&gt;数百英里长的海堤&lt;/a&gt;，一切应有尽有。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-s